{"result": {"folders": ["lab1"], "nr": 654, "data": {"embed_links": []}, "created": "2016-03-04T01:19:30Z", "bucket_order": 3, "no_answer_followup": 0, "change_log": [{"uid": "i0c9nvk0xzc2n3", "anon": "no", "when": "2016-03-04T01:19:30Z", "data": "ild0jvk36ia16e", "type": "create"}, {"to": "ild0jvk12mj16d", "uid": "i76z9sx78G8", "anon": "no", "when": "2016-03-04T01:25:43Z", "data": "ild0rvp1grr6oe", "type": "i_answer"}, {"uid": "hdjonbiyfs62ie", "anon": "no", "when": "2016-03-04T01:29:13Z", "data": "ild0wdp7e2xco", "type": "i_answer_update"}, {"to": "ild0jvk12mj16d", "uid": "i0c9nvk0xzc2n3", "anon": "no", "when": "2016-03-04T01:40:59Z", "type": "followup"}, {"to": "ild0jvk12mj16d", "uid": "hdjonbiyfs62ie", "anon": "no", "when": "2016-03-04T01:57:12Z", "type": "feedback"}, {"to": "ild0jvk12mj16d", "uid": "ie7xy4gmt1p1pp", "anon": "no", "when": "2016-03-04T14:52:06Z", "type": "followup"}, {"to": "ild0jvk12mj16d", "uid": "i0gl5kctugw3xi", "anon": "no", "when": "2016-03-05T14:08:45Z", "type": "feedback"}, {"to": "ild0jvk12mj16d", "uid": "hdjonbiyfs62ie", "anon": "no", "when": "2016-03-05T14:29:10Z", "type": "feedback"}], "bucket_name": "Today", "history": [{"anon": "no", "uid": "i0c9nvk0xzc2n3", "subject": "内核栈、用户栈的问题", "created": "2016-03-04T01:19:30Z", "content": "<p>老师上课说内核栈和用户栈要分开是考虑到安全的原因。网上说每次进程从用户态进入内核态的时候&#xff0c;得到的内核栈都是空的。那这样的话&#xff0c;进入内核态时&#xff0c;直接把用户栈当作内核栈就可以啦呀&#xff1f;</p>"}], "type": "question", "tags": ["lab1", "student"], "tag_good": [{"role": "instructor", "name": "Yong XIANG", "endorser": {}, "admin": true, "photo": null, "id": "hdjonbiyfs62ie", "photo_url": null, "us": false, "class_sections": ["课程设计_i5j09fnsl7k5x0", "清华学生_i5j09fnsl7k5x0", "所有老师和助教_i5j09fnsl7k5x0", "os2018spring_i5j09fnsl7k5x0"], "facebook_id": null}], "unique_views": 213, "children": [{"folders": [], "data": {"embed_links": []}, "children": [], "created": "2016-03-04T01:25:43Z", "bucket_order": 3, "tag_endorse": [], "bucket_name": "Today", "id": "ild0rvow89f6od", "history": [{"anon": "no", "uid": "hdjonbiyfs62ie", "subject": "", "created": "2016-03-04T01:29:13Z", "content": "<p>用户栈可以由用户代码来填写东西&#xff0c;而内核栈只有内核代码能够获取&#xff0c;所以会有安全的说法。如果直接把用户栈当作内核栈&#xff0c;那可能用户会注入恶意代码在栈中。</p>"}, {"anon": "no", "uid": "i76z9sx78G8", "subject": "", "created": "2016-03-04T01:25:43Z", "content": "<p>用户栈可以由用户代码来填写东西&#xff0c;而内核栈只有内核代码能够获取&#xff0c;所以会有安全的说法。如果直接把用户栈当作内核栈&#xff0c;那可能用户会注入恶意代码在栈中。</p>"}], "type": "i_answer", "tag_endorse_arr": [], "config": {}, "is_tag_endorse": false}, {"anon": "no", "folders": [], "data": {"embed_links": null}, "no_upvotes": 0, "subject": "<p>用户没机会注入恶意代码吧&#xff0c;因为内核代码认为现在的内核栈是空的。</p>", "created": "2016-03-04T01:40:59Z", "bucket_order": 213, "bucket_name": "Week 2/28 - 3/5", "type": "followup", "tag_good": [], "uid": "i0c9nvk0xzc2n3", "children": [{"anon": "no", "folders": [], "data": {"embed_links": null}, "subject": "<p>注入恶意代码的可能性存在于使用用户栈。分开就没有可能了。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>这是一个好问题&#xff0c;希望更多的同学参与讨论。也许这会是考试题目中的一个。</p>", "created": "2016-03-04T01:57:12Z", "bucket_order": 213, "bucket_name": "Week 2/28 - 3/5", "type": "feedback", "tag_good": [], "uid": "hdjonbiyfs62ie", "children": [], "tag_good_arr": [], "id": "ild1wcrom726gm", "updated": "2016-03-04T01:57:12Z", "config": {}}, {"anon": "no", "folders": [], "data": {"embed_links": null}, "subject": "<p>感觉没有直接针对suanrong同学问题的回答。</p>\n<p>我理解的suanrong同学的问题是&#xff1a;如果内核态每次进入的时候都是空的&#xff0c;那么可以推定内核态中运行的程序不会使用任何栈上已经存在的内容。因此&#xff0c;即便内核态使用用户态的栈&#xff0c;且用户栈中的确注入了恶意代码&#xff0c;内核程序也会因为认为栈是空的&#xff0c;而不会调用到这些恶意代码。</p>", "created": "2016-03-05T14:08:45Z", "bucket_order": 213, "bucket_name": "Week 2/28 - 3/5", "type": "feedback", "tag_good": [], "uid": "i0gl5kctugw3xi", "children": [], "tag_good_arr": [], "id": "ilf7h019fuhse", "updated": "2016-03-05T14:08:45Z", "config": {}}, {"anon": "no", "folders": [], "data": {"embed_links": null}, "subject": "<p>进入内核态的可能存在多种。其中一些情况下&#xff0c;进入时相应内核栈可能不空。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>如果有兴趣&#xff0c;可尝试列出进入内核的可能情况&#xff0c;并分析这时相应内核栈的情况。</p>", "created": "2016-03-05T14:29:10Z", "bucket_order": 213, "bucket_name": "Week 2/28 - 3/5", "type": "feedback", "tag_good": [], "uid": "hdjonbiyfs62ie", "children": [], "tag_good_arr": [], "id": "ilf878rzbpt1vj", "updated": "2016-03-05T14:29:10Z", "config": {}}], "tag_good_arr": [], "no_answer": 0, "id": "ild1bihuh294kz", "updated": "2016-03-04T01:40:59Z", "config": {}}, {"anon": "no", "folders": [], "data": {"embed_links": null}, "no_upvotes": 0, "subject": "<p></p><ul><li>我认为是因为用户栈无法保证是“可用的”&#xff0c;比如用户进程因为堆栈设置错误导致异常而进入内核&#xff0c;这是如果使用用户堆栈会出错。</li><li>而用户级进程不可能破坏tss中的内核栈指针&#xff0c;更不能破坏内核栈的数据。</li></ul>", "created": "2016-03-04T14:52:06Z", "bucket_order": 213, "bucket_name": "Week 2/28 - 3/5", "type": "followup", "tag_good": [], "uid": "ie7xy4gmt1p1pp", "children": [], "tag_good_arr": [], "no_answer": 0, "id": "ildtkw9nxhqg0", "updated": "2016-03-04T14:52:06Z", "config": {}}], "tag_good_arr": ["hdjonbiyfs62ie"], "no_answer": 0, "id": "ild0jvk12mj16d", "config": {}, "status": "active", "drafts": null, "request_instructor": 0, "request_instructor_me": false, "bookmarked": 9, "num_favorites": 2, "my_favorite": false, "is_bookmarked": false, "is_tag_good": false, "q_edits": [], "i_edits": [], "s_edits": [], "t": 1643168259136, "default_anonymity": "no"}, "error": null, "aid": "kyuzyf5sx1047v"}